snippet.textDisplay: Coke Studio Pakistan was always famous for introducing new talents and producing live shows. Although this season got the former part right, it completely replaced the live performances with pre-recorded songs. Now these videos are more or less like any other music video on Youtube. Coke Studio always excelled at producing mesmerising live music performances, therefore, it is quite sad to see these prerecorded songs. Don't get me wrong, I love the actual vocals but the videos aren't just working for me.
